Definition: the branch of optics that deals with the use of coherent light from a laser in order to make a hologram that can then be used to create a three-dimensional image
Synonyms: optics, the, branch, of, that, deals, with, use, coherent, light, from, a, laser, in, order, to, make, hologram, can, then, be, used, create, three-dimensional, image
Category: noun.cognition
